## Installation

Using pip, you can install the latest stable release:

```
pip install ANNarchy
```

## Platforms

* GNU/Linux
* MacOS X

## Dependencies

* g++ >= 6.1 ( >= 7.4 recommended ) or clang++ >= 3.4
* python >= 3.7 with development files
* cython >= 0.20
* setuptools >= 40.0
* numpy >= 1.13
* sympy >= 1.6
* scipy >= 0.19

Recommended:

* matplotlib
* lxml 
* PyQtGraph 
* pandoc 
* tensorboardX
